## What's Raycast?
<Divider />

If you've ever used MacOS Spotlight or Windows Start, imagine that, but much more powerful! At it's core,
Raycast allows you to launch apps by searching up their name, but you can extend what it can do with extensions.

You can:
- check your email with Raycast
- open GitHub issues
- control your playlist
- set your window layouts
- anything you can code

