### 1. Build your extension

Come up with an idea and get building! Check our MacOS or Windows guides if you need help getting started.

The official Raycast Developer documentation covers a ton more stuff in detail!

> To Windows users: Raycast on Windows is still in private beta, but we have exclusive invite codes for Hack Clubbers. Once you've gotten your idea, request a code here:

