You need have at least 3 hours of tracked time spent on your project. Add another feature, polish up what you already have!

### 2. Ship it!

Once you've finished building and polished up your extension, make sure you've met the submission requirements:
- 3+ hours of coding tracked on Hackatime
- Source code is public on GitHub
- You have a README with a description, demo video (screen recording), and installation instructions

Fill out the form to submit!

